\usepackage{upgreek}
\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}$$\vartheta^{2}=2/3\sum {\vartheta_{ij}^2}. $$\end{document} The components ϑij are obtained from the measured RDCs, e.g. by singular value decomposition (SVD) (Losonczi et al. 1999), using a set of equations1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
\usepackage{upgreek}
